{"tid":572096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反槍狗惡夢]拼死同持械賊駁火 母女合力守住酒舖","createTime":"2018-02-25T09:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T15:16:40.000Z","uid":33481,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98669c712b302a0378859e6200075323e086c8c1","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180225/57872475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872475&d=nwB2E2dYtjwmbrruhglyTgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=49ed3a3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872475&h=999b22a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180225/57872475</a><br />\n<br />\n 美國俄克拉何馬州一間酒舖遭持械劫匪光顧，看舖的母女奮力抵抗，與對方駁火。<br />\n<br />\n36歲蒙面劫匪蒂龍李（Tyrone Lee），上周四晚持槍闖入塔爾薩（Tulsa）酒舖，指嚇店內53歲女子蒂娜林（Tina Ring）及其30歲女兒阿什莉李（Ashley Lee），要求交出現款。母女在收銀處取錢給蒂龍，但趁對方不為意時按掣將舖門鎖上，然後取出藏於櫃枱下的手槍，跟蒂龍一搏。<br />\n<br />\n蒂娜向蒂龍連開多槍，阿什莉在母親掩護下報警。蒂龍一度離開，之後返回櫃台後，中槍的他那時似乎無槍在手，於是強搶蒂娜的手槍，而阿什莉那時向蒂龍開槍，蒂龍搶去蒂娜的的槍後試圖向阿什莉近距離還火，卻發現子彈已耗盡。他身中多槍，最後負傷自行離開，駕車入院求醫，已被人工昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n蒂娜頭部割傷，需要縫針。她表示，最初一心保護女兒，給對方錢了事，豈料對方回頭，唯有與他一拼。<br />\n<br />\n事發時不在城內的酒舖33歲老闆賈斯廷克里斯蒂安（Justin Christian），大讚看舖的媽媽和妹妹英勇抗賊，令他自豪。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，蒂龍與區內多宗械劫案有關。蒂龍雖然活過來的機會很大，但康復後肯定要接受法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果禁左槍，呢兩母女唔知會點呢？"},{"pid":"3e528f797940d2e2bda6aabd07cc8e416e0c1431","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"同場加映：無槍港人勇武反抗都無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GPvq20XDoCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGPvq20XDoCU&d=nwB2E2dYtjwmbrruhglyTgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=da0d5a62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GPvq20XDoCU</a>"},{"pid":"e2109978b3fc3c33f34966960e4526d1e92502c5","tid":572096,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"個記者係現場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4ae42af64a521fb3004b661ae4b9817c3aeacd","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e2109978b3fc3c33f34966960e4526d1e92502c5","tid":572096,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"個記者係現場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"記者緊係唔係現場啦，不過你原來盲既"},{"pid":"8d3aaff6515112fcb7fca8b9f0fdce73ba1a60e1","tid":572096,"uid":51828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcf38b500fa6f649bb9ef7cda881308a839e174","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d3aaff6515112fcb7fca8b9f0fdce73ba1a60e1","tid":572096,"uid":51828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"美國平民勇過差佬<br />\n差佬打份工只識恰9黑人<br />\n<br />\n偏偏反槍狗不斷要求平民禁槍，只有廢物差佬有資格有槍<br />\n一邊反TRUMP一邊要求TRUMP武裝獨大唔知咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b329a5bdbf974e4c8f657d5b517256e61c1d4825","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時班反槍狗唔見曬"},{"pid":"4505870ae5b5710173973d8f8cb062b5cf11a04f","tid":572096,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"反槍狗只係一班懦夫，懦夫就算有槍都會投降<br />\n但如果其他人有槍成功反抗既話就會顯出佢既懦弱<br />\n因此，佢地要大家都無槍反抗唔到，不斷將無力感擴大<br />\n令自己由懦弱變成「